short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes your extremely good adult son even better

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension changes "adult son" to "large adult son" across the web. No longer must we guess at the size of your incredible boy! Now, his bounty is evident to us all.

This extension is free and was created using 9to5 Google's "How-to: Make your own text-replacing Chrome extension like ‘Millennials to Snake People’" 
Special thanks to Nick Pedroso for debugging.
